author: brane
msg: Get the tests working on Windows again, now that the client can print
file names in the local path style.
Note: This is only a temporary hack; once the client consistently outputs
paths like that, and consistently accepts them, too, a better solution can
be found.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/trans_tests.py,
subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/schedule_tests.py: Convert os.sep to / in
svn's output before comparing that to the expected output.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/svntest/tree.py (create_from_path):
Convert os.sep to / before splitting the path.

author: brane
msg: Make the generator work correctly on a clean checkout.
* build/generator/gen_win.py (WinGeneratorBase.__init__): Create getdate.c
from getdate.cw if it doesn't exist, so that it gets included in the
project file.

author: brane
msg: Neon depends on an xml parser.
* build.conf (neon): Add dependency on xml.
